FrontEnd.name: Digital Nomads
FrontEnd.description: Discover top-notch accommodations tailored for digital nomads. Find high-speed internet, inspiring workspaces, and ideal settings to work and explore the world. Maximize productivity while living your best digital nomad life!

FrontEnd.name: Space X
FrontEnd.description: Explore our website for a concise summary of past SpaceX launches, all pulled from an API. Dive into mission launches, rockets and results. Relive the excitement of SpaceX's historic missions in just a few clicks!
